## MP2a declaration (submitted; see deltas above)

Full text: **`Week 8/MP2a.md`**. Summary:

### 1. Problem

Personal constellations on real stars â€” draw a shape, geometric match to catalog, AI-generated name.

### 2. Audience (MP2a wording)

Non-experts + educators/communicators. **Build audience** is listed in **Build decisions** (public + hobbyists + artists).

### 3. Data (MP2a)

HYG v4.2, `mag < 6.5`, static CSV client-side; fields include ra, dec, mag, ci, spect, lum, proper name. MP2a also described full constellation rows in Supabase â€” **build uses optional name registry only** unless the user expands scope.

### 4â€“6. Track, platform, rationale

**Design track.** **Lovable** + **Claude edge function**. **Supabase** in MP2a for persistence â€” **optional names-only in build**. Browser-side matching on ~9k stars; no compute backend required.

