## What we are building

A **deployed creative tool** for the **general public**, **hobbyists**, and **artists**: immersive **galaxy / night-sky** with **~8,835â€“9,000** HYG stars (`mag < 6.5`); **straight-line sketch pad** â†’ **vertex snap** to real stars on the map; text description â†’ **Claude** name; **2D first**, **pan/zoom**, **3D toggle**; **PNG export**. Optional Supabase table for **used names** only.

**Not in scope unless the user explicitly asks:** full constellation database, share-by-slug, accounts/login, 119k unfiltered HYG in browser, classical-constellation editor.

