## Architecture: lean split

| Layer | Where | Responsibility |
|--------|--------|------------------|
| **Data prep** | Repo â€” `Week 8/` | Filter HYG, precompute `x/y/z`, export **`stars_visible.csv`** for client load. |
| **Product** | **Lovable** | Star map, sketch pad (polyline), snap + overlay, 2D/3D, Claude naming edge function, **PNG export**. |
| **Persistence** | **Optional Supabase** | **`used_names`** (or equivalent) only â€” not required for MP2 minimum. |
| **Docs** | Repo | `README.md`, `mp2.md`, `MP2a.md`, optional `CONSTELLATION_MAPPING.md`. |

Sync Lovable export into repo for graders. **Never** commit API keys or Supabase service role.

