## Data source and pipeline

- **Source:** `MP1/MP1 for Pandas Stars file.csv`  
- **Filter:** `mag < 6.5` (~8,835 stars)  
- **Reference:** `MP1/mp1b_visualizations.ipynb`  
- **Client file:** `Week 8/stars_visible.csv` â€” `id`, `ra`, `dec`, `mag`, `ci`, `spect`, `lum`, `proper`, `dist`, `x`, `y`, `z`  
- **Prep:** `prepare_stars.py` (document in README)  
- **Integrity:** Real HYG only; MP1-style checks (Sol, distance sentinels)

