## Visual / UX direction

- Immersive **galaxy**; **geometric**, **futuristic**; **Roboto Mono**.  
- Speak to **curious public**, **hobbyists**, **artists** â€” no jargon on primary controls.  
- Accessible contrast; matched stars visually distinct from field.

